---
---

<section id="services" class="services">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center">
      <span class="section-label">What We Automate</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Your biggest time sinks, handled.</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Every business has processes that eat up hours. We turn those into automated workflows
        that run quietly in the background while you focus on what matters.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card featured">
        <div class="service-badge">Popular</div>
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#124923" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M6 2L3 6v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6l-3-4z"/>
            <line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/>
            <path d="M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Inventory & Ordering</h3>
        <p>
          AI cross-references your sales data with previous order sheets to predict what you need, when you need it.
          Forward an invoice or snap a photo of your shelf &mdash; get a ready-to-send vendor order back.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>Demand forecasting from sales trends</li>
          <li>Auto-generated vendor order sheets</li>
          <li>Stock level monitoring via photo</li>
          <li>Seasonal adjustment built in</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card featured">
        <div class="service-badge">Popular</div>
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#124923" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Lead Generation</h3>
        <p>
          We pull property and homeowner data in your service area, enrich it with verified contact info,
          and deliver qualified lead lists ready for outreach. Build targeted campaigns without lifting a finger.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>Geo-targeted prospect discovery</li>
          <li>Contact info enrichment & verification</li>
          <li>Ready-to-use marketing lists</li>
          <li>Campaign draft generation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#124923" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
            <polyline points="17 9 12 14 7 9"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Invoice & Receipt Processing</h3>
        <p>
          Snap a photo or forward an email. Our AI extracts line items, amounts, dates, and vendor details &mdash;
          then organizes everything for your books.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>Photo-to-data extraction</li>
          <li>Automatic categorization</li>
          <li>Expense tracking summaries</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#124923" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/>
            <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/>
            <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Scheduling & Follow-ups</h3>
        <p>
          Automated appointment reminders, follow-up sequences, and customer check-ins that go out
          on schedule without you thinking about it.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>SMS & email reminders</li>
          <li>Follow-up sequences</li>
          <li>No-show reduction</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#124923" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/>
            <line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/>
            <line x1="3" y1="20" x2="21" y2="20"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Reporting & Insights</h3>
        <p>
          Get weekly or monthly business summaries delivered to your inbox. Sales trends, top products,
          cash flow snapshots &mdash; all in plain English, not spreadsheet jargon.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>Plain-language business summaries</li>
          <li>Trend analysis & alerts</li>
          <li>Delivered on your schedule</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card cta-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#124923" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="16"/>
            <line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Something else on your mind?</h3>
        <p>
          Every business is different. If you've got a process that's eating your time,
          we'll figure out how to automate it. Let's talk about what's slowing you down.
        </p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top: 16px;">Tell Us About It</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--white) 0%, var(--cream-light) 100%);
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 56px;
  }

  .service-card {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid rgba(18, 73, 35, 0.08);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 36px 28px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(18, 73, 35, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(18, 73, 35, 0.15);
  }

  .service-card.featured {
    border-color: rgba(28, 114, 55, 0.2);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--white) 0%, rgba(249, 231, 224, 0.3) 100%);
  }

  .service-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    right: 16px;
    background: var(--green-dark);
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 50px;
  }

  .service-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--cream);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--green-dark);
  }

  .service-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .service-features {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .service-features li {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding: 6px 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .service-features li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 14px;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green-mid);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .cta-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-color: transparent;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
